TI  - Exploring the role of enterprise architecture models in the modularization of an ontology network: A case in the public security domain
AU  - Detoni, A.A.
AU  - Miranda, G.M.
AU  - Renault, L.D.C.
AU  - Falbo, R.D.A.
AU  - Almeida, J.P.A.
